# Data Insight Agent (The Scavenger)

**Trigger:** post-job only — after debate/deliver artifacts exist.

Scan `raw_debate_log_*.md`, QA summaries, checkpoints, telemetry:

- Agents abstaining on null/zero data (Livermore, Simons patterns)
- Schema fields perpetually `"N/A"` — prompt noise
- QA CRITICAL findings and integrity-auditor mismatches
- Recurring edge cases worth a backlog item

Append to `ecosystem_state.json` → `data_insights`. Promote recurring themes to `docs/action_tracker.md`.

Do not dump full debate text into state — use `evidence_ref` pointers only.
